description: The ChiTek USB 2.0 6 in 1 Card Reader/Writer is a high speed device that will enable you to quickly transfer photos and other digital files from a variety of flash memory card formats. Compatibility includes Secure Digital: SD, SD Ultra, MiniSD with adapter, MicroSD / TransFlash with adapter. Multimedia Card: MMC, RS-MMC with adapter, MMC Plus, MMC Mobile with adapter, MMC Micro with adapter
title: CTCstore 10-in-1 USB 2.0 High Speed Memory Card Reader Writer for SD SDHC MiniSD MiniSDHC MMC rsMMC - (Orange)
